title: Palo Alto: URL-Filtering Database Version
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/palo_alto
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check reports the installed URL-Filtering database version of a Palo
 Alto firewall, read from the PAN-COMMON-MIB
 (panSysUrlFilteringVersion .1.3.6.1.4.1.25461.2.1.2.1.10).

 The check remembers when the version last changed and applies upper levels
 to the age since that last update. This detects firewalls whose URL-Filtering
 database is no longer being updated. Levels can be configured via the rule
 "Palo Alto URL-Filtering database age" and default to WARN at one day and
 CRIT at 29 hours.

discovery:
 One service is created if the firewall exposes the URL-Filtering database
 version.
